abstract: The U.K.-based grocery chain Tesco said it halted production at a factory in China on Sunday after a British newspaper reported the factory used forced labor to produce charity Christmas cards for the supermarket.
snippet: The U.K.-based grocery chain Tesco said it halted production at a factory in China on Sunday after a British newspaper reported the factory used forced labor to produce charity Christmas cards for the supermarket.
lead_paragraph: LONDON — The U.K.-based grocery chain Tesco said it halted production at a factory in China on Sunday after a British newspaper reported the factory used forced labor to produce charity Christmas cards for the supermarket.
headline_main: Tesco Halts Work at Chinese Factory Over Prison Labor Claim
headline_print_headline: Tesco Halts Work at Chinese Factory Over Prison Labor Claim

abstract: French President Emmanuel Macron, whose plans to reform the pension system have run into fierce public opposition, will forego a special presidential pension payout when he eventually steps down, his office said on Sunday.
snippet: French President Emmanuel Macron, whose plans to reform the pension system have run into fierce public opposition, will forego a special presidential pension payout when he eventually steps down, his office said on Sunday.
lead_paragraph: PARIS — French President Emmanuel Macron, whose plans to reform the pension system have run into fierce public opposition, will forego a special presidential pension payout when he eventually steps down, his office said on Sunday.
headline_main: France's Macron to Give Up Presidential Pension in Reform Gesture
headline_print_headline: France's Macron to Give Up Presidential Pension in Reform Gesture

abstract: A magnitude 5.0 earthquake struck southwest Iran on Sunday, the semi-official ISNA news agency reported.
snippet: A magnitude 5.0 earthquake struck southwest Iran on Sunday, the semi-official ISNA news agency reported.
lead_paragraph: GENEVA — A magnitude 5.0 earthquake struck southwest Iran on Sunday, the semi-official ISNA news agency reported.
headline_main: Magnitude 5.0 Earthquake Hits Southwestern Iran: ISNA, USGS
headline_print_headline: Magnitude 5.0 Earthquake Hits Southwestern Iran: ISNA, USGS

abstract: Russia's Foreign Minister Sergei Lavrov said on Sunday that Russia was prepared to include the heavy Sarmat missile and the Avangard hypersonic missile in a new START strategic arms reduction treaty, should it be extended, Interfax reported.
snippet: Russia's Foreign Minister Sergei Lavrov said on Sunday that Russia was prepared to include the heavy Sarmat missile and the Avangard hypersonic missile in a new START strategic arms reduction treaty, should it be extended, Interfax reported.
lead_paragraph: MOSCOW — Russia's Foreign Minister Sergei Lavrov said on Sunday that Russia was prepared to include the heavy Sarmat missile and the Avangard hypersonic missile in a new START strategic arms reduction treaty, should it be extended, Interfax reported.
headline_main: Russia Ready to Include 'Super Weapons' in Arms Control Treaty: Ifax Cites Lavrov
headline_print_headline: Russia Ready to Include 'Super Weapons' in Arms Control Treaty: Ifax Cites Lavrov

abstract: Hey, it looks like the government won’t shut down this year! Let’s count our economy’s blessings. Next week will be a pretty slow one for business and tech (aside from the post-holiday shopping frenzy, of course), but 2020 promises all kinds of surprises. Enjoy the calm while it lasts, and happy holidays.
lead_paragraph: Hey, it looks like the government won’t shut down this year! Let’s count our economy’s blessings. Next week will be a pretty slow one for business and tech (aside from the post-holiday shopping frenzy, of course), but 2020 promises all kinds of surprises. Enjoy the calm while it lasts, and happy holidays.
